Link copied to clipboard
common
class TagPlaceObject4 : TagPlaceObject3, IDisplayListTag
Content copied to clipboard
PlaceObject4 is essentially identical to PlaceObject3 except it has a different swf tag value of course (94 instead of 70) and at the end of the tag, if there are additional bytes, those bytes will be interpreted as AMF binary data that will be used as the metadata attached to the instance.
